p:
Gene sequence comparison and homology analysis were performed with DNAMAN software (version 5.1.0.0; Lynnon Biosoft), according to the software instructions. MEGA software (version 4.0; 
 https://www.megasoftware.net/) was used to construct phylogenetic trees with neighbor joining and a Kimura 2-parameter model. The bootstrap value was 1,000. All of the reference strain sequences were derived from GeneBank (
 https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed).
